{"id":408829,"title":"03 | 如何设计课程结构与逻辑","content":"","comments":[{"had_liked":false,"id":346261,"user_name":"Neu","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1901854,"ip_address":"","ucode":"48F8C312B94999","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1d/05/1e/02245834.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1652950123,"is_pvip":true,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":2,"score":2,"product_id":100085401,"comment_content":"最简单的展示、沟通结构：总、分、总。\n容易出现的问题：只有分，只有总和分。\n总：给课程目标定下完整的基调，否则会非常发散。核心点是什么，后面讲解的每一个点，都围绕核心讲，而不是由一个点到另一个点发散的过程。\n日常表达和沟通也一样，都要注意聚焦，不要发散和跳跃。\n总：核心观点，奠定展示基调。\n分：逐级展开，加数字强提醒。\n总：总结提炼，核对重要信息。\n\n沟通表达过程中的一些小技巧：\n沟通问题要及时、直接、有效。逻辑能够带来效率，一定要提前准备。\n提出问题要简明扼要、触及本质、直击核心诉求。\n讨论解决方案时要充分信任，不提假设和不可控的因素。\n回应解决方案要干脆利索、阐明后果。\n对事不对人，沟通不带抱怨情绪。\n\n基础展示逻辑\n导、讲、复、测\n导：回顾、故事、场景\n导入的目的，是让听众进入一种准备开始学习的场域或状态。\n讲：取舍、详略、顺序\n复：重点、难点、要点\n测：落实、效果、改变","like_count":4},{"had_liked":false,"id":374663,"user_name":"jo","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1622897,"ip_address":"上海","ucode":"A9D507236F8CBC","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/18/c3/71/e7990e80.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1684291478,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100085401,"comment_content":"结构：总分总\n逻辑：导、讲、复、测","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":374611,"user_name":"jo","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1622897,"ip_address":"上海","ucode":"A9D507236F8CBC","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/18/c3/71/e7990e80.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1684229526,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100085401,"comment_content":"总分总逻辑结构：\n核心观点\n逐级展开 数字加强提醒\n总结提炼","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":374596,"user_name":"jo","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1622897,"ip_address":"上海","ucode":"A9D507236F8CBC","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/18/c3/71/e7990e80.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1684216276,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100085401,"comment_content":"主体目标：因材施教\n知识容量：最近发展区(确定已达到的水平和可能达到的水平)，下限到上限不断突破\n干湿比例：调剂节奏\n顺序结构：导、讲、复、测","like_count":0}]}